item.title: MIFV Interview Series: Shawn Pryor - Author of Kaiju Unleashed, The Gamer and Power Rangers Comics
item.description: Nathan sits down with a fellow another fellow author! This time it’s the writer of the new book Kaiju Unleashed, Shawn Pryor. Not only did he write this crash course in all things tokusatsu, he’s also created his own toku-inspired comic book, written for Boom Studios’ Power Rangers comics, and written children’s books. We have a lot to talk about! Feed: https://feed.podbean.com/monsterislandfilmvault/feed.xml
